---

<CategoryLayout
  category={category}
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
  canonicalURL={canonicalURL}
  icon="calculator"
  color="ocean"
  tagline="Quick answers to everyday math questions"
  calculators={calculators}
>
  <p>
    Our everyday calculators solve the small math problems that pop up in daily life.
    Whether you're splitting a dinner bill, figuring out a discount, or wondering how
    old your dog is in human years, these tools give you instant answers.
